{
  "stem": "15943.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I speak to other people, it just seems to me, like, they had, like, a routine, like, this, this-- do this on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would have buckets with stones at the end of a field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would fill in those buckets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First, there were empty buckets-- fill them up with the stones, carry them to the other end of the field, dump them out, fill them up, and bring them back again.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would curse us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would swing their whips, sometimes hitting people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They just-- and-- with less strength.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Where the day that we're supposed to rest, we would carry those things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Otherwise, they would go into the barracks and search.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are they searching for, if we have any treasures?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we're hiding something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If-- and the girls, when we were-- they were searching, we would always hide my poems in the straw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are always-- if there's somebody in the barracks-- and we never knew when they're going to-- all of a sudden, they're surrounded by-- and can start searching.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would hide the, the-- those poems on their body, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was part of the entertainment out to the park-- the barracks, so they could search.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few months, just a few months, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, [SIGHS] we were taken-- we hoped-- we hoped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We believed that they're taking us to dig ditches because we, you know, ditches were always in different places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then a guard came and started arguing with the ones in front leading the columns and saying that the Russian Army is right behind them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were arguing because they had orders to take us to the woods to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were some of them that wanted to follow the orders.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
